<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id60069be2-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58" identifier="/us/usc/t30/s541g"><num value="541g">§ 541g.</num><heading> Rules and regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Interior is authorized to issue such rules and regulations as may be necessary or appropriate to effectuate the purposes of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id60069be3-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-11/ch795/s8">Aug. 11, 1955, ch. 795, § 8</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/69/681">69 Stat. 681</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
